### Health
GET http://localhost:4000/health

### Create
POST http://localhost:4000/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "테스트 상품",
  "description": "설명입니다",
  "price": 12000,
  "tags": ["중고"]
}

### Get list
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products?offset=0&limit=10&sort=recent&q=설명

### Get detail
GET http://localhost:4000/api/products/REPLACE_WITH_ID

### PATCH
PATCH http://localhost:4000/api/products/REPLACE_WITH_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 15000,
  "tags": ["전자"]
}

### Delete
DELETE http://localhost:4000/api/products/REPLACE_WITH_ID
